OL,3,CThe path to the World Cup: Will Wales
OL,4,Cmake it to Brazil?
OL,6,FWales will have to beat some familiar
OL,7,Ffaces if they are to make it to next
OL,8,Fyear's Women's World Cup in Brazil.
OL,10,FToday, in Switzerland, the draw for
OL,11,Fplay-off phase of qualifying was made
OL,12,Fand now Wales' route to a first ever
OL,13,Fglobal gathering is laid out.
OL,15,FBy going undefeated and winning their
OL,16,Fgroup in League B, Wales did
OL,17,Feverything they could to secure
OL,18,Fthemselves as favourable a draw as
OL,19,Fpossible. In the first play-off, Wales
OL,20,Fwill face Albania in October, with the
OL,21,Fsecond leg being played in Wales.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/7
