OL,3,CThe path to the World Cup: Will Wales
OL,4,Cmake it to Brazil?
OL,6,FThe two sides faced each other in the
OL,7,Fgroup stage of qualifying, with Wales
OL,8,Fwinning 4-0 at home and 1-0 away. They
OL,9,Fwill be confident heading into this
OL,10,Ftie.
OL,12,FThings get interesting when it comes
OL,13,Fto play-off number two. Wales will
OL,14,Fface the winner of Romania v Norway.
OL,15,FWith the latter's vastly superior
OL,16,Franking, Wales would likely face
OL,17,Fanother familiar face if they get
OL,18,Fthrough to this stage of the play-offs.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/7
