OL,3,CThe path to the World Cup: Will Wales
OL,4,Cmake it to Brazil?
OL,6,FNorway's manager is Gemma Grainger,
OL,7,Fwho was in charge of Wales between the
OL,8,Fyears of 2021 and 2024 before she left
OL,9,Ffor Scandinavia.
OL,11,FPersonal histories aside, it would be
OL,12,Fa huge challenge for Wales. Norway
OL,13,Fhave gone through a difficult period
OL,14,Fbut are historically one of the
OL,15,Fpowerhouses of European football.
OL,17,FThey are currently ranked 14th in the
OL,18,Fworld with Wales down in 31st, which
OL,19,Fillustrates the size of the task. This
OL,20,Ftwo-legged tie will take place in
OL,21,FNovember and December.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
