OL,3,CThe path to the World Cup: Will Wales
OL,4,Cmake it to Brazil?
OL,6,FSpeaking after the draw, manager Rhian
OL,7,FWilkinson said: "Some people get,
OL,8,Fmaybe on paper, an easier route. Some
OL,9,Fpeople have a more challenging one.
OL,11,F"In the end you get what you get and
OL,12,Fyou have to deliver on the day.
OL,14,F"So yes, it could have been harder. It
OL,15,Fcould have been easier, it could have
OL,16,Fbeen all these things. This is the one
OL,17,Fthat we got.
OL,26,@oD@QOUsD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/7
