PN,43805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1781894897
OL,3,CThe path to the World Cup: Will Wales
OL,4,Cmake it to Brazil?
OL,6,F"If we want to be a country that makes
OL,7,Fmajor tournaments, then we have to be
OL,8,Fable to confidently show up against
OL,9,Fteams ranked higher than us and know
OL,10,Fthat we're going to put in a strong
OL,11,Fperformance.
OL,13,F"We've got to keep building that, to
OL,14,Fkeep climbing and Norway may be a
OL,15,Fgreat challenge for us. But equally, I
OL,16,Fthink it's a really great opportunity."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@gO]
