OL,3,CThe path to the World Cup: Will Wales
OL,4,Cmake it to Brazil?
OL,6,FBy the end of the play-off process,
OL,7,Fthere will be eight winners but just
OL,8,Fseven automatic qualification spots.
OL,9,FThe lowest-ranked winner after two
OL,10,Fties will have to play in an
OL,11,FIntercontinental play-off match
OL,12,Fagainst a team from another continent.
OL,14,FThis would be a one-off match, with
OL,15,Fthe winner heading to the World Cup.
OL,17,FIf Wales got this far, it's highly
OL,18,Flikely - barring any other major
OL,19,Fupsets - that they would end up in
OL,20,Fthis third play-off tie.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/7
